      "content": "i know they love me, i do... but love doesn't change the fact that i'm just an extra weight they have to carry every day. i look at them and all i see is more stress because of me. wouldn't it just be kinder if i wasn't even a factor anymore? if i just weren't around to cause all this trouble?",
